<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a8Aug1937"><font color="red">8 August 1937</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I hope Mr Joyce will not collapse working so extremely hard, as you say he is, to finish <i>W.i.P.</i> by February 2nd, 1938. </div>
